Syntax <wield [weapon] (in [limb])>

This command allows you to wield a weapon for use in combat.
The limb is the limb in which you want to wield it.

ex: wield battleaxe

You can also specify the limb you want to wield it to, like
ex: wield battleaxe in left hand

if its a two handed sword you specify two limbs to wield it to, like
ex: wield battleaxe in left hand and right hand
